fix.fixtext:
Configure proper file permissions:
1. Set library permissions: chmod 644 /usr/local/lib/libwolfssl.so* 2. Set provider permissions: chmod 644 /usr/local/openssl/lib64/ossl-modules/wolfprov.so 3. Set config permissions: chmod 644 /etc/ssl/openssl.cnf 4. Set nginx config: chmod 644 /etc/nginx/nginx.conf 5. Set script permissions: chmod 755 /docker-entrypoint.sh 6. Set private key: chmod 600 /etc/nginx/ssl/*.key 7. Remove world-writable: find / -type f -perm -002 -exec chmod o-w {} \;
Rebuild container with proper file permissions.
